membership:
SKAL is a active member of the Federation of Finnish Enterprises FFE (Suomen Yrittajat) and International Road Transport Union IRU and an associated member of Nordic Logistics Association NLA. &#xd;
&#xd;
SKAL also cooperates closely with the Confederation of Finnish Industries EK and participates actively in the work of European Union SME organization UEAPME. &#xd;
&#xd;
SKAL has close relations and cooperation with several  road transport associations from various member states as well as with large number of other lobbying organizations in Brussels.

